---
// No props needed for this static component
---
<section class="bg-neutral-900 py-20">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-gray-200 mb-12">
      Müşterilerimiz Ne Diyor?
    </h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 pt-10">
      <!-- Testimonial 1 -->
      <div class="bg-neutral-900 p-8 rounded-xl border border-red-900/50 relative">
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2">
          <img class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full object-cover border-4 border-neutral-900" src="https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/women/68.jpg" alt="Ayşe Yılmaz">
        </div>
        <div class="pt-10 text-center">
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-400 italic mb-4">"Bu araç sayesinde veri analiz süreçlerimiz %50 hızlandı. İnanılmaz bir verimlilik artışı!"</p>

          <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-200">Ayşe Yılmaz</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Pazarlama Müdürü</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- Testimonial 2 -->
      <div class="bg-neutral-900 p-8 rounded-xl border border-red-900/50 relative">
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2">
          <img class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full object-cover border-4 border-neutral-900" src="https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/men/32.jpg" alt="Mehmet Kaya">
        </div>
        <div class="pt-10 text-center">
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-400 italic mb-4">"Teknik bilgim olmamasına rağmen, platformu rahatlıkla kullanabiliyorum. Arayüzü çok sezgisel."</p>

          <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-200">Mehmet Kaya</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">KOBİ Sahibi</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- Testimonial 3 -->
      <div class="bg-neutral-900 p-8 rounded-xl border border-red-900/50 relative">
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2">
          <img class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full object-cover border-4 border-neutral-900" src="https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/women/44.jpg" alt="Fatma Demir">
        </div>
        <div class="pt-10 text-center">
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-400 italic mb-4">"Raporlama özellikleri harika. Karar alma süreçlerimizde artık çok daha veriye dayalı ilerliyoruz."</p>

          <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-200">Fatma Demir</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Veri Analisti</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
